{"tid":500759,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"第一次去大板 !!! 正阿!!","createTime":"2017-12-16T06:12:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-19T09:54:30.000Z","uid":133829,"like":3,"dislike":153,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"3b9b895920806d422820c44794cafaf2ea335df3","tid":500759,"uid":133829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:12:59.000Z","msg":"第一次去大板，我地大學grad trip咁去，一行4個人主要都想以最平既方式玩最多既野，當然要買廉航啦，所以就分成唔同航空。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/140445_f3cc473cbd001e20c168269734816512.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F140445_f3cc473cbd001e20c168269734816512.png&h=5d782bd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n-&gt;去程: 捷星航空 (桃園中正機場出發)<br />\n<br />\n-&gt;回程: 樂桃航空 (大板關西機場出發)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/140525_384a0ab186732ca4546dafa18d1934a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F140525_384a0ab186732ca4546dafa18d1934a4.png&h=800c3ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好大部高達阿!!!<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n係香港托朋友搵左間民宿，民宿不錯，個業主好好人阿，知我係由朋友介紹， 比出很多意見和幫助， 不得不畀十個讚 !! 問番朋友先知，原來他有唔少民宿， 有心齋橋，道頓崛。 佢真係好好人為我地提供 屋內視頻睇啱我才book，佢都好想我地唔會有後悔的旅程。大家如果鍾意可以whatsapp +85297559647 。而我今次住那間民宿位於日本橋道頓堀。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/140558_c59d53564f0ce00f262f9a7b777a004e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F140558_c59d53564f0ce00f262f9a7b777a004e.png&h=461065bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n經過長長既走廊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/140559_f0540bc8d3576b121f181b88e186ce88.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F140559_f0540bc8d3576b121f181b88e186ce88.png&h=4e57706c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/140600_958f882633f3b2b1e0ea045b0e99102a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F140600_958f882633f3b2b1e0ea045b0e99102a.png&h=dd57fa5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入面有間大房，有2張雙人床， 兩張單人床褥 。啱曬我地6個人住。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/140601_9e41b8eaed4395d88bc4c96710c63648.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F140601_9e41b8eaed4395d88bc4c96710c63648.png&h=399c4f9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大房入面都有靚靚茶几，幾高檔既格調。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/140601_6b9161df72879b2dc11496757885b562.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F140601_6b9161df72879b2dc11496757885b562.png&h=bd928264&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有獨立洗手間。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/140602_e088275acd029ffa5b283b011c3f72ba.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F140602_e088275acd029ffa5b283b011c3f72ba.png&h=b207adbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n獨立浴室，入面有花灑同浸浴，照顧唔同需要。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/140603_9b73f49be21cd4e3f80f81ce8c0ea278.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F140603_9b73f49be21cd4e3f80f81ce8c0ea278.png&h=50babbea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n廚房設計，收埋係門既另一面，非常節省位置。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/140604_6ebcbcf9b6888f620184737e17f360d0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F140604_6ebcbcf9b6888f620184737e17f360d0.png&h=14a94307&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓下係黑門市場，行過點就係道頓堀入口，旅遊客必到的地方，行去日本橋站5行分鐘，去難波都只是15分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/140605_420b236e6dba3d4c191937b1e03ea015.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F140605_420b236e6dba3d4c191937b1e03ea015.png&h=00f6b8d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n道頓堀絕對係美食購物天堂，先係依到食個下午茶，去完心齋橋晚上再回來吃大餐。喜歡購物的到24小時營業的激安之殿堂朝聖，食既有天婦羅﹑ 炸串﹑ 大阪燒﹑ 章魚燒﹑ 拉麵﹑全蟹宴， 反正依到集合左好多地道美食! 商店大概9點關門, 不過食既都開到很晚，簡直係個不夜天。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n我地去左Universal Studio JAPAN 日本環球影城，依個主題樂園以荷里活電影為主題，加入左日本卡通人物元素，仲新增左全球熱爆既哈利波特區。依到大把野玩，想黎既準備係依到用成天瘋狂玩樂啦! 上網買Klook電子門卷可以省去不少排隧門票時間， 早D入場玩機動遊戲!<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/140607_08c36b216af073091f3eb40f4fa11096.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F140607_08c36b216af073091f3eb40f4fa11096.png&h=9970a4ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n環球影城門口<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/140610_a9054fd188fbe07e685dea00d3f42abb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F140610_a9054fd188fbe07e685dea00d3f42abb.png&h=44bdf0c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好恐怖既巨人阿!!<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/140611_1b9f3e3ed708e557eb4fcb91f72cf55a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F140611_1b9f3e3ed708e557eb4fcb91f72cf55a.png&h=efa003a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n哈利波特區既魔法學園<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/140612_002c5ed193c71f68e3bba5be5581133b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F140612_002c5ed193c71f68e3bba5be5581133b.png&h=87ee0049&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n夜晚去心齋橋依間可麗餅食。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/140612_f42a0b5afc9818a0ca1b1298ce52a7d2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F140612_f42a0b5afc9818a0ca1b1298ce52a7d2.png&h=923a5ed2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大板城緊係一定要去啦。大阪城係大阪市的地標，日本三大名城之一。現存既天守閣係第二次世界大戰被摧毀後再重建既模樣，現為大阪城歷史博物館，票價600円(持大阪周遊券免費)。大阪城公園往天守閣走時會經過櫻花林。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由於日本橋 有近鐵直接去到奈良 所以行程最後一天我們去了 奈良睇鹿仔，見到班鹿仔實在太好動，大概依日係咁影相， 他們會衝來問你攞食物 ， 可在 小檔 以100日元購買鹿餅，經驗很難忘， 很值得。<br />\n<br />\n最後只有幾張比較正常吧XDD<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/140613_04a81fc34c5878bbacd42d6a508c0574.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F140613_04a81fc34c5878bbacd42d6a508c0574.png&h=8ddf0c31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（意外捕捉到迷你小鹿喝奶的畫面！）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/140613_171cb77e301df2b38a8db3ee8f40e248.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F140613_171cb77e301df2b38a8db3ee8f40e248.png&h=65c9fdc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我地往東大寺前進，據說佢係全日本腹地最大的寺廟。果然，行左好幾個大門，總算比我地見識到寺廟本尊，非常有設計感既建築！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/140615_5933f40e0815f77f81f6e58055aa3539.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F140615_5933f40e0815f77f81f6e58055aa3539.png&h=3588ea1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望提供大家去大阪自由行時，更多參考的方向！"},{"pid":"a1fb07891a7ee39a08661d32ad2ef0bca2713c14","tid":500759,"uid":16528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:23:09.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"d9e65b5bff4168eabb5264c9884f0ccaa91451fa","tid":500759,"uid":105033,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:27:54.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"0ce544b9e0c1b75f303401db7a35e2fca8b3e140","tid":500759,"uid":50980,"